Package: bedcaster
Title: Bed Occupancy Forecasting for Epidemics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Finlay", "Campbell", email = "finlaycampbell93@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Forecast ETU and isolation bed occupancy during epidemics with a
    Bayesian Stan model that nowcasts and projects cases, deaths, alerts,
    and healthcare demand from daily surveillance data.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/finlaycampbell/bedcaster
